  "critical": false,
  "description": "Forge welding, brazing, soldering, riveting, oxy-acetylene welding and cutting, and arc welding (SMAW/stick) with flux-coated electrodes. Also covers advanced processes: TIG (GTAW) for stainless/aluminum/titanium, MIG (GMAW) for high-deposition fabrication, resistance spot and seam welding, electron beam welding in vacuum, ultrasonic welding and wire bonding for semiconductor packaging, friction stir welding for aluminum alloys, laser welding (CO₂ and fiber), and diffusion bonding for dissimilar metals and UHV components.",
